{"base_path":"/","components":null,"consumes":"[\"application/json;charset=UTF-8\",\"application/json\"]","definitions":{"ServerImageResponse":{"properties":{"arch":{"description":"**参数解释**:服务器镜像架构类型。\n**取值范围**:\n- ARM\n- X86","enum":["ARM","X86"],"example":"X86","type":"string"},"image_id":{"description":"**参数解释**:服务器镜像ID。\n**取值范围**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。","maxLength":64,"minLength":1,"type":"string"},"name":{"description":"**参数解释**:服务器镜像名称。表示服务器镜像的名称。\n**约束限制**:不涉及。\n**取值范围**:1 - 256字符\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","maxLength":256,"minLength":1,"type":"string"},"server_type":{"description":"**参数解释**:服务器类型。\n**取值范围**:\n- BMS:裸金属服务器\n- ECS:弹性云服务器\n- HPS:超节点服务器","enum":["BMS","ECS","HPS"],"example":"ECS","type":"string"},"status":{"description":"**参数解释**:服务器镜像状态。\n**取值范围**:\n- ACTIVE\n- INACTIVE","type":"string"}},"title":"ServerImageResponse","type":"object"}},"description":null,"group_id":"ade740e866904a7dbdaa5ec0f538d4d0","host":"modelarts.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com","id":"a51025cb07cf4363838b5846832174fc","info_version":"v1","method":"get","name":"GetDevServerImage","parameters":{"projectId":{"description":"用户项目ID。获取方法请参见[获取项目ID和名称](modelarts_03_0147.xml)。","in":"path","name":"project_id","required":true,"type":"string"}},"paths":{"/v1/{project_id}/dev-servers/images/{id}":{"get":{"description":"查询Lite Server镜像详情接口用于获取指定Lite Server镜像的详细信息。该接口适用于以下场景:当用户需要了解某个Lite Server镜像的具体配置和属性,以便在创建或调整Lite Server实例时选择合适的镜像时,可以通过此接口获取相关信息。使用该接口的前提条件是用户已登录并具有查询镜像详情的权限,且指定的镜像已存在。查询操作完成后,接口将返回指定Lite Server镜像的详细信息,包括镜像ID、名称、操作系统、版本、创建时间等。若用户无权限操作、指定的镜像不存在或镜像ID无效,接口将返回相应的错误信息。","operationId":"GetDevServerImage","parameters":[{"description":"**参数解释**:镜像ID。\n**约束限制**:^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$。\n**取值范围**:不涉及。\n**默认取值**:不涉及。","in":"path","name":"id","required":true,"type":"string"},{"$ref":"#/parameters/projectId"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"**参数解释**:镜像详情。","schema":{"$ref":"#/definitions/ServerImageResponse"}}},"summary":"查询Lite Server镜像详情","tags":["Lite Server管理"],"x-api-type":"open-api","x-apiexplorer-hide":"N","x-is-registered":"Y","x-open-region-cloud":"hk,hc,hcso","x-order":32,"x-publish-doc":"Y","x-request-examples-url-1":"GET https://{endpoint}/v1/{project_id}/dev-servers/images/{id}","x-support-sdk":"N"}}},"product_short":"ModelArts","region_id":"cn-north-4","schemes":["HTTPS"],"security_definitions":{"ApiTokenAuth":{"in":"header","name":"X-Auth-Token","type":"apiKey"}},"summary":"查询Lite Server镜像详情","tags":"Lite Server管理","uri":null,"version":"2.0"}